Well, unfortunately,
the alternatives

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:33.840
have pain points as well.

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:37.600
This is no means trying to
bash on these particular ones.

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:39.200
I'm not--Beaver Builder,

00:06:39.200 --> 00:06:41.440
Divi, Elementor,
they're, you know,

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:43.200
they have some
good aspects to it,

00:06:43.200 --> 00:06:45.920
but really, they're most
commonly used.

00:06:45.920 --> 00:06:47.200
They're high up there.

00:06:47.200 --> 00:06:48.880
And they also
have similar issues,

00:06:48.880 --> 00:06:53.280
so ATAG, you know, really about
being able to easily traverse so

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:55.840
people with disabilities
can create content.

00:06:55.840 --> 00:06:57.200
They have problems
with this as well.

00:06:58.240 --> 00:06:59.760
Beaver Builder is
trying to improve,

00:06:59.760 --> 00:07:02.240
you know, but it takes
time and it's been years.

00:07:03.200 --> 00:07:06.560
And so, you know, it's nice that
there's a change of pace and

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:08.960
really focusing on it but
they still have problems.

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:13.120
Then of course, Divi and other
people have even built plugins

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:15.840
to fix some of the front-end
issues of what's being created.

00:07:16.880 --> 00:07:18.240
But CampusPress built that

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:21.520
and it still has
problems too, right?

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:24.800
'Cause there's a lot of work
involved if you start with,

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:26.880
you know, sometimes
not the right basis.

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:30.800
And then Elementor, you know,
they're also advocating about

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:34.080
accessibility but it
also has some work to do.

00:07:35.280 --> 00:07:36.400
So you can even take a look.

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:40.960
You've got GitHub aspects that
are pointing out multiple issues

00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:42.800
and it's because, yeah,
it's not one and done,

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.560
and there's always
room for improvement.

