Okay, so, Nick, you're not
really making it sound amazing.

00:07:49.920 --> 00:07:52.960
Maybe there's plugins, maybe
there's something to fix that.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:56.560
But really, all
page builder tools,

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:59.440
all plugins, they
all still need work.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:04.480
So we've got a nice background
here of a road in Japan pretty

00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:05.600
much in front of a Family Mart.

